        {
            "title": "美伊新一輪會談可能在數日內舉行——《華爾街日報》",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DrJikYRxD9K5.sZYFOVJ3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEE1R1IN_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com——據《華爾街日報》援引知情官員報導,在伊斯蘭堡馬拉松式會談未能達成協議後,地區國家正努力促使美國和伊朗重返談判桌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱,進一步外交的大門仍然敞開,第二輪會談可能在數日內舉行。地區政府也正與華盛頓磋商,以延長週二晚間宣布的為期兩週的脆弱停火協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊斯蘭堡會議標誌著自1979年以來美國和伊朗官員之間最高級別的面對面接觸。週六,美伊在伊斯蘭堡進行了長達21小時的直接會談,但未能達成協議。副總統JD·萬斯表示,華盛頓已明確表達條件,但德黑蘭拒絕接受。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3631b094-c75f-379f-8fea-24a5cce67a06-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》今天稍早報導,美國的要求包括全面停止伊朗的鈾濃縮活動、拆除主要核設施、交出高濃縮材料、重新開放霍爾木茲海峽且不收取通行費、實現更廣泛的地區和平,以及停止支持包括真主黨和胡塞武裝在內的代理組織。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情官員表示,伊朗官員提議允許有限度的濃縮活動或減少其濃縮鈾庫存,但雙方未能彌合分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗議會議長穆罕默德·巴格爾·卡利巴夫週日宣布,伊朗不會屈服於威脅,此前川普總統宣布美國將封鎖霍爾木茲海峽。卡利巴夫在社交媒體上直接向川普表示:\"如果你開戰,我們就應戰。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國將從4月13日美國東部時間上午10:00開始對進出伊朗港口的海上交通實施封鎖。美國中央司令部表示,封鎖將適用於所有國家前往伊朗港口和沿海地區的船隻,包括波斯灣和阿曼灣沿岸的設施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%B0-%E8%BC%AA%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%87%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E6%95%B8%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-222522795.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-13 06:36:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新加坡股市接近回到歷史高位 戰爭增強其避險吸引力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/b.NPItXWl.YnkcjVBzkMVQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d59ac43c2acc3897aae8c1cc43fdfb5b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 新加坡股市接近回到歷史高位，在全球市場動盪之際，該國資產被視為避風港。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自伊朗戰爭2月爆發導致全球能源價格飆升以來，新加坡股市在亞太地區受到的衝擊最小。在新加坡元相跑贏其他東南亞貨幣的幫助下，新加坡股市有望成為自戰爭爆發以來首個再創新高的亞洲主要市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過美國和伊朗周末未能達成協議，美國總統唐納德·川普表示，美國將開始全面封鎖霍爾木茲海峽，為新一輪全球市場動盪埋下伏筆。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"635\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eVnDMfDjagy.1NDp_SRInw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c6fe3415d8f73a6ff73619491b4044d7\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">海峽時報指數與戰爭開始時基本持平，而MSCI亞洲指數下跌4.9%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e492d4fe-a750-33fe-9ee6-f5c7adc2e15b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Singapore Stocks Near Record High as War Fuels Haven Status (1)</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
